                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980523-33-defend325 t17980523-33-punish176"></join>
               Confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17980523-33-punish177" type="punishmentDescription">
