                     <interp inst="t17980523-33-punish177" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980523-33-defend325 t17980523-33-punish177"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice GROSE.</p>
